snippet.title: AsteroidShooter VR Promo
snippet.description:
VR space shooter. Destroy the asteroids, do the missions and get reward.

You will go from a simple pilot to hardened warrior, the destroyer of asteroids and hordes of enemy ships.
May the force be with you!

GooglePlay - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wooloofun.asteroidshooter
AppStore - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/asteroid-shooter-vr/id1201838536?ls=1&mt=8
